{"tid":752271,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"90後咩都唔識第一次布吉包膠","createTime":"2018-07-22T16:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T06:20:44.000Z","uid":162772,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"90a9781ee57ae1b06f8b4bae1b9d8d673b228320","tid":752271,"uid":162772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"工作關係成日周圍去，但同官人去旅行十隻手指數曬，今次放假諗住去北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但官人話成L日去日本死港女（9月會再去沖繩）<br />\n咁去東南亞lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前年去左峴港<br />\n個Resort好很正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 官人話想陽光與海灘<br />\n咁就簡左布吉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好興奮Book完機票 先發覺7月係布吉雨季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係連個天都唔鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多兩日 布吉沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有Weather Forcast都話哥幾日都係狂風暴雨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁...煮到埋黎都要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如是者五日四晚貨不對辦狂風暴雨布吉之旅都要上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b98fdb5613dbcc724eb51312d28e3a22926a86","tid":752271,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33c1fc261812e6f9e9fa9341bc56b194923ba4aa","tid":752271,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"布吉無tour 同無去旅行無分別"},{"pid":"8b5b5df5a0b9caa248eeaca7e272866f7e77eb6d","tid":752271,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5b98fdb5613dbcc724eb51312d28e3a22926a86","tid":752271,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:33:31.000Z","msg":"我要"},{"pid":"d8fd347e32a21fe433b3bf271e9c56ef64c6d02d","tid":752271,"uid":162772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:45:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>第一日包膠</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出發哥日再check weather <br />\n好D啦 Shower + cloudy 都要收貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上機前食個早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/001712_bdbf65fb753f9e59db2720f7088b1f54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F001712_bdbf65fb753f9e59db2720f7088b1f54.png&h=be2b8104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上機啦 今次搭因龍早機<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/001855_3b5bdd83a511cc1557ae34c86530b098.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F001855_3b5bdd83a511cc1557ae34c86530b098.png&h=bcc35bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/001857_55ec665dc42c1c2779efe8b0809883f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F001857_55ec665dc42c1c2779efe8b0809883f8.png&h=3680fc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇Delay,空姐空少都好好service<br />\n 不過飛機餐就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算啦<br />\n差唔多3個鐘就到布吉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/002323_7442b780da19083e8c465ef75110cea6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F002323_7442b780da19083e8c465ef75110cea6.png&h=dbce8e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>說好的狂風大暴雨呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n天氣超好 成個海都係李斯德林色 我賺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<del>五日既forcast都係雷/雨 但5日夾埋10鐘雨都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </del><br />\n出到機場上左Book定既車，個plan 包埋sim 卡 ，快靚正唔洗去到又買呢又買路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一二晚住芭東山（patong hill) <br />\n一間新開左冇兩年既五星酒店<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/003023_7df157f6a00c7514c0296b577235186d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F003023_7df157f6a00c7514c0296b577235186d.png&h=4a6b136a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCheckin 姐姐比杯百香果welcome drink <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n有條冰凍薄荷毛巾比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/003311_80d5aea719e7f9cfbb462e51455d9537.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F003311_80d5aea719e7f9cfbb462e51455d9537.png&h=61e78676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放低野游個水 個池冇咩景 勝在夠新<br />\n酒店新 minibar免費 但員工就唔夠主動<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/003500_10097fefe7deddfda6cd5b44a183fe18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F003500_10097fefe7deddfda6cd5b44a183fe18.png&h=60c7b571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n游完水 就搭酒店免費Shuttle去江西冷後面個海鮮市場搵野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n檔仔有炒粉飯面 串燒海鮮 炸蟲蟲都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香蕉Pancake椰子雪糕食到肚炸都唔洗500 B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/004341_8bd55513bfb83ea6195da7cdc8387e2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F004341_8bd55513bfb83ea6195da7cdc8387e2f.png&h=63ba4305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一日圓滿結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1269684e79c81f0cd4af777755ff0b1a2a8da31","tid":752271,"uid":162772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5b98fdb5613dbcc724eb51312d28e3a22926a86","tid":752271,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"我男友"},{"pid":"f9a20ba5f8d769eecc135851133272a662326b9f","tid":752271,"uid":162772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T17:36:06.000Z","msg":"第二日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身一早上網用左K字頭個apps book左去皇帝島加珊瑚島，但臨出發前一日下晝先收到E-mail話 Trip has been cancel due to extreme weather<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去布吉冇島去咁我去黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nemail 曬旅遊公司同K字頭公司 冇回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我唯有打上去泰國當地負責人 大家都係半桶水英文之下得出一個結論係：聽日咩島都冇得去 退錢把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我望住個天咁藍 心諗唔_係掛 天氣惡劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係我灰心之際有個<del>身材飽滿高挑</del>既泰國大媽問我係咪想<del>睇人妖</del>join tour<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOMG<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 緊係啦 不過我都要收番起我雙眼發亮哥下 扮下格下價先啦 佢都好老實，自己先斬一半 我再還價 2200B 最後1000B 成交 <br />\n雖然貴過網上book 少少 不過好過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二日食個酒店早餐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/011354_5b52d0a81a86da8579f04180eb1200ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F011354_5b52d0a81a86da8579f04180eb1200ed.png&h=17a50349&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/011355_b24d1d6b866b31e5142174d8753145fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F011355_b24d1d6b866b31e5142174d8753145fa.png&h=01e57765&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/011357_a7e8f182c3ac860daec7de0b2c43a159.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F011357_a7e8f182c3ac860daec7de0b2c43a159.png&h=5b11a8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n選擇同味道都一般般 餓唔死但唔會好好食<br />\nStaff 仲搞笑 我地係餐廳門口等左5分鐘都冇人<br />\n行入去Staff問完我地咩房就走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我地坐邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己搵位 自已叫啡茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐，旅遊車黎接我地去碼頭集合登船 <br />\n20個人一隻船 大約30分鐘到皇帝島<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢30分鐘係我人生中最接近海盜船既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD浪好大 好似玩緊海盜船咁 D浪好高 海水不停潑埋黎 其實我覺得好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但同行有老有幼 ，有團友嘔 小朋友嚇到呆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雨季出海要顧及老幼，如果唔舒服既話大家都唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/011820_5f2756a1bd49774fe5ee0468c7a03c39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F011820_5f2756a1bd49774fe5ee0468c7a03c39.png&h=f2cb626c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到又一個李斯德林 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皇帝島話係以前皇帝渡假用既 依家開放埋比你<del>地班蟻民</del>同樂<br />\n係靚既 不過好大浪 <br />\n上水後有三個option:<br />\n1.浮潛<br />\n2.水肺潛水<br />\n3.上海灘休息<br />\n我同官人原本打算去珊瑚島玩水中漫步<br />\n但肥仔導遊哥哥話珊瑚島天氣唔好去唔到<br />\n<del>仲好啦我唔想再玩多次海盗船</del><br />\n肥仔哥哥話我地可以去水肺潛水 唔洗牌都玩得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁潛水Lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/013522_259945303e4900d69bdf0a37174c9306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F013522_259945303e4900d69bdf0a37174c9306.png&h=99408731&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63220f4bfc265096a4b17f297141282aa23d302f","tid":752271,"uid":103319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T07:24:46.000Z","msg":"好正咁 打算十二月去 不過實好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6660e473eb8e807e0b72253daddd13467b07c6e9","tid":752271,"uid":161992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T18:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>第一日包膠</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出發哥日再check weather <br />\n好D啦 Shower + cloudy 都要收貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上機前食個早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/001712_bdbf65fb753f9e59db2720f7088b1f54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F001712_bdbf65fb753f9e59db2720f7088b1f54.png&h=be2b8104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上機啦 今次搭因龍早機<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/001855_3b5bdd83a511cc1557ae34c86530b098.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F001855_3b5bdd83a511cc1557ae34c86530b098.png&h=bcc35bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/001857_55ec665dc42c1c2779efe8b0809883f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F001857_55ec665dc42c1c2779efe8b0809883f8.png&h=3680fc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇Delay,空姐空少都好好service<br />\n 不過飛機餐就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算啦<br />\n差唔多3個鐘就到布吉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/002323_7442b780da19083e8c465ef75110cea6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F002323_7442b780da19083e8c465ef75110cea6.png&h=dbce8e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>說好的狂風大暴雨呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n天氣超好 成個海都係李斯德林色 我賺左[img]assets/faces/dog/haha.gif[/img] <br />\n<del>五日既forcast都係雷/雨 但5日夾埋10鐘雨都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </del><br />\n出到機場上左Book定既車，個plan 包埋sim 卡 ，快靚正唔洗去到又買呢又買路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一二晚住芭東山（patong hill) <br />\n一間新開左冇兩年既五星酒店<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/003023_7df157f6a00c7514c0296b577235186d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F003023_7df157f6a00c7514c0296b577235186d.png&h=4a6b136a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCheckin 姐姐比杯百香果welcome drink <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n有條冰凍薄荷毛巾比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/003311_80d5aea719e7f9cfbb462e51455d9537.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F003311_80d5aea719e7f9cfbb462e51455d9537.png&h=61e78676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放低野游個水 個池冇咩景 勝在夠新<br />\n酒店新 minibar免費 但員工就唔夠主動<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/003500_10097fefe7deddfda6cd5b44a183fe18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F003500_10097fefe7deddfda6cd5b44a183fe18.png&h=60c7b571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n游完水 就搭酒店免費Shuttle去江西冷後面個海鮮市場搵野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n檔仔有炒粉飯面 串燒海鮮 炸蟲蟲都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香蕉Pancake椰子雪糕食到肚炸都唔洗500 B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/004341_8bd55513bfb83ea6195da7cdc8387e2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F004341_8bd55513bfb83ea6195da7cdc8387e2f.png&h=63ba4305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一日圓滿結束[img]assets/faces/dog/touch.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n酒店咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a7dd06d6e83cdc625dd9d0e881ae37307f5c9b","tid":752271,"uid":27708,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T19:37:33.000Z","msg":"D 中文差到唔知講乜<br />\n00後都無咁衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7e8b1c2347f31c3c09a0d866fdee49ff495c0d","tid":752271,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:29:44.000Z","msg":"咩叫官人"},{"pid":"6e8a339a5d01753ec7bd1111ecfb598c300878af"